name: __ECommonUserPrivilegeResult
doc: Enum giving specific reasons why a user may or may not use a certain privilege

Unknown: State is unknown and needs to be queried
Available: This privilege is fully available for use
UserNotLoggedIn: User has not fully logged in
LicenseInvalid: User does not own the game or content
VersionOutdated: The game needs to be updated or patched before this will be available
NetworkConnectionUnavailable: No network connection, this may be resolved by reconnecting
AccountTypeRestricted: Account does not have a required subscription or account type
AccountUseRestricted: Another account/user restriction such as being banned by the service
